          {
            "do": "stub",
            "member": "text",
            "return": "second"
          },
          {
            "do": "invoke",
            "member": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      "expected_output": "value=second\n"
    }
  ]
}

Here are the public test cases for feature2_4_stub_per_argument:
